marketing-text: E wehe i kahi kahua kumu no ka ikepili COVID19. Nā kime pākela nui me ka hōʻanoʻike browser a me REST API kikoʻī kikoʻī, kahi i hoʻopaʻa ʻia i nā ʻōlelo āpau.
go-to-the-dashboard: E hele i ka pale kahua

highest-death-rate: ʻO ka make nui o ka make nui
view-all-stats-by-country: E nānā i nā ʻōkuhi āpau e kēlā me kēia ʻāina
name: Tagu inoa
promo-message: Hana ʻia me ke aloha ❤️ e ka hui ma Hoobu.com. E hoʻolālā i kāu huakaʻi post-pandemic i kēia manawa me kā mākou mea hoʻokūkū huakaʻi hoʻoikaika wā maoli maoli nō
general-advice-wash-hands-description: Holoi pinepine i kou mau lima a no 20 kekona me ka hoʻohana ʻana i ka wai a me ka wai ma hope o ka puhi ʻana o kou ihu, mai ka umu a ʻā paha ma mua o ka ʻai ʻana a mālama paha i ka meaʻai. ʻO ka holoi ʻana ʻo ka lima kūpono loa i ka make ʻana o nā maʻi.
general-advice-minimise-contact-descript: Hoʻololi i nā hālāwai koʻikoʻi a me nā huakaʻi a e ʻimi i nā koho ʻē aʻe e like me nā lūlū lima, hana nui a honi paha.
general-advice-avoid-face-description: Hiki i nā lima ke ʻohi i nā maʻi a i nānā ʻia ka lima, hiki ke hoʻopili i nā lima i nā maʻi i kou mau maka, ihu a waha ʻole paha. Mai ia manawa, hiki i ka huakaʻi ke komo i loko o kou kino a maʻi ʻoe iā ʻoe.
general-advice-be-hygienic-description: Ka uhi ʻana i kou waha a me ka ihu me kou ʻoki kuʻekuʻe a i ʻole ʻawaʻī e inu a ʻūʻū paha ʻoe, a e kāpae koke i ka kikoʻī i hoʻohana ʻia.
general-advice-self-isolate-title: Luana mai nei? Hū kaʻawale iā ʻoe iho!
general-advice-self-isolate-description: Inā hoʻomohala ʻoe i ka maʻi e like me nā hōʻailona e pono ʻoe e hoʻokaʻawale iā ʻoe iho ma ke ʻano he hana mālama a pale i ka hopena o ka hoʻolaha ʻana i ka maʻi ma o ka noho ʻana i ka home.
